%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fstudent-loans%2Fhow-to-find-college-grants%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPell%20Grant%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20graduation%2C%20I%20worked%20in%20the%20fashion%20industry%20for%20around%20a%20year.%20But%20I%20realized%20that%20career%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Egrowth%20in%20fashion%2C%20specifically%20design%2C%20was%20incredibly%20slow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20I%20had%20always%20wanted%20to%20study%20marketing.%20I%20figured%20that%20having%20a%20master's%20degree%20would%20give%20me%20an%20edge%20because%20I%20would%20know%20how%20to%20design%20clothes%20and%20market%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20I%20started%20looking%20into%20schools%20in%20New%20York.%20I%20looked%20at%20Columbia%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eand%20New%20York%20University%20but%20soon%20realized%20that%20I%20couldn't%20afford%20to%20go%20to%20either%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eeven%20if%20I%20got%20accepted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETuition%20at%20NYU's%20Stern%20School%20of%20Business%2C%20for%20example%2C%20costs%20over%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.stern.nyu.edu%2Fprograms-admissions%2Ffull-time-mba%2Ffinancial-aid%2Ftuition-cost-attendance%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%2480%2C000%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20year%20%E2%80%94%20my%20kidney%20couldn't%20pay%20for%20that.%20I%20had%20gotten%20through%20college%20with%20no%20debt%20and%20wanted%20to%20do%20the%20same%20for%20my%20master's%20degree.%20I%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmore-american-students-avoid-debt-studying-abroad-college-europe-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erealized%20I%20needed%20to%20find%20another%20option%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22eb4bf495-4d05-4e93-ada3-26ab55a81151%5C%22%3EI%20decided%20to%20start%20looking%20elsewhere%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20favorite%20retailers%20have%20always%20been%20Dollar%20Tree%2C%20Burlington%2C%20Marshalls%2C%20TJ%20Maxx%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fikea-first-time-visit-most-surprising-things-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIkea%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20love%20knickknacks%20and%20how%20Ikea%20manages%20to%20create%20organized%20chaos.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20love%20for%20Ikea%20inspired%20me%20to%20look%20up%20colleges%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerican-dad-in-sweden-shares-differences-in-schools-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESweden%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20country%20where%20the%20furniture%20brand%20was%20founded.%20In%20the%20span%20of%20two%20weeks%2C%20I%20researched%20all%20of%20the%20requirements%2C%20sent%20everything%20in%20and%20that%20was%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20few%20of%20the%20parameters%20that%20I%20set%20limited%20my%20options.%20The%20classes%20needed%20to%20be%20taught%20in%20English%2C%20and%20I%20was%20only%20interested%20in%20one-year%20programs%20because%20I%20didn't%20have%20enough%20funds%20to%20sustain%20myself%20for%20two%20years.%20The%20options%20I%20found%20were%20M%C3%A4lardalen%20University%20and%20Stockholm%20University.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20got%20into%20M%C3%A4lardalen%20University%20in%20V%C3%A4ster%C3%A5s%2C%20a%20city%20an%20hour%20and%20a%20half%20away%20from%20Stockholm.%20I%20remember%20screaming%20with%20joy%20when%20I%20got%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20honestly%20didn't%20hit%20me%20that%20I%20was%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsweden-work-life-balance-american-expat-happiness-burnout-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESweden%3C%2Fa%3E%20until%20I%20was%20on%20a%20shuttle%20bus%20heading%20to%20the%20school.%20Growing%20up%20in%20Brooklyn%2C%20as%20the%20oldest%20of%20seven%20siblings%2C%20it%20was%20a%20breath%20of%20fresh%20air%20to%20live%20on%20my%20own%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20my%20life.%20I%20didn't%20feel%20scared%2C%20and%20I%20could%20adapt%20to%20the%20new%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e86862fa-65dd-4986-a18c-46e1985add4a%5C%22%3EI%20could%20travel%20often%20in%20Sweden%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fswedish-woman-moved-to-us-found-attitude-to-ambition-different-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emoving%20to%20Sweden%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20I%20had%20only%20traveled%20outside%20the%20US%20once%20to%20visit%20London.%20But%20while%20I%20was%20living%20in%20Europe%2C%20I%20traveled%20at%20least%20once%20every%20two%20months%20to%20countries%20like%20Germany%2C%20Estonia%2C%20Denmark%2C%20and%20Finland.%20I%20could%20catch%20a%20flight%20with%20a%20friend%20and%20go%20somewhere%20for%20two%20or%20three%20days%20before%20we%20flew%20back%20for%20classes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20girl%20reading%20a%20book%20in%20front%20of%20the%20Eiffel%20Tower%20in%20Paris.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F672b19a688cea3ba1c1e9b0e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWebb%20enjoyed%20being%20able%20to%20travel%20easily%2C%20including%20a%20trip%20to%20Paris%2C%20while%20studying%20in%20Sweden.%3Cp%3EOmarni%20Webb%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20loved%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-to-sweden-from-the-us-culture-shock-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esafety%20of%20living%20in%20Sweden%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20was%20a%20complete%20change%20from%20living%20in%20New%20York%2C%20where%20I%20constantly%20had%20to%20be%20aware%20and%20look%20over%20my%20shoulder.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20never%20worried%20about%20walking%20outside%20in%20the%20early%20hours.%20I%20remember%20walking%20home%20from%20a%20friend's%20party%20in%20the%20dark%2C%20late%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eat%20night.%20The%20cops%20pulled%20me%20over%2C%20and%20they%20gave%20me%20a%20reflector%20slap%20bracelet%20so%20that%20I%20could%20be%20seen%20in%20the%20d