0undid%20nationwide%20abortion%20protections%20and%20allowed%2013%20states%20to%20pass%20laws%20that%20effectively%20banned%20abortion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20Trump%20took%20credit%20for%20ending%20the%20decadeslong%20precedent%20of%20legalized%20abortion%20nationwide.%20%26quot%3BI%20did%20it%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-abortion-roe-v-wade-supreme-court-gop-primary-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EI'm%20proud%20to%20have%20done%20it%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BNobody%20else%20was%20going%20to%20get%20that%20done%20but%20me%2C%20and%20we%20did%20it%2C%20and%20we%20did%20something%20that%20was%20a%20miracle.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%2024%20hours%20after%20Election%20Day%2C%20Wisp%20said%20it%20saw%20a%201%2C650%25%20increase%20in%20new%20patients%20purchasing%20emergency%20contraception.%20There%20was%20a%20600%25%20increase%20in%20medication%20abortion%20sales%20and%20a%2050%25%20increase%20in%20birth%20control%20sales.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20Wisp's%20reproductive%20health%20sales%20(of%20emergency%20contraception%2C%20birth%20control%2C%20and%20medication%20abortion%20products)%20doubled%20compared%20to%20the%20week%20prior%20to%20the%20election%2C%20the%20company%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20expect%20that%20momentum%20to%20sustain%20over%20the%20next%20few%20weeks%20and%20months%2C%26quot%3B%20Cepak%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20purchases%20came%20from%20women%20in%20both%20anti-abortion%20states%20as%20well%20as%20states%20with%20widespread%20access%20to%20reproductive%20healthcare.%20Emergency%20contraception%20purchases%20surged%20in%20Texas%2C%20Indiana%2C%20and%20Oklahoma%2C%20where%20there%20are%20strict%20restrictions%2C%20but%20sales%20also%20increased%20in%20states%20like%20California%20and%20New%20York.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDespite%20being%20states%20where%20reproductive%20rights%20are%20fully%20protecte