uced%20the%20SATHEE%20initiative%20to%20offer%20free%20guidance%20for%20competitive%20exams.%20SATHEE%20provides%20various%20resources%2C%20such%20as%20reference%20video%20lectures%2C%20mock%20tests%2C%20and%20additional%20materials%20to%20aid%20in%20exam%20preparation.%20However%2C%20participation%20in%20the%20SATHEE%20program%20does%20not%20guarantee%20success%20in%20any%20exam%20or%20admission%20to%20any%20institution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20online%20platform%20has%20been%20created%20to%20assist%20students%20in%20preparing%20for%20competitive%20exams%2C%20including%20JEE%2C%20NEET%2C%20SSC%2C%20IBPS%2C%20ICAR%2C%20and%20CUET.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnStudents%20can%20access%20the%20platform%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsathee.iitk.ac.in%2F%5C%22%3Esathee.iitk.ac.in%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20through%20the%20SATHEE%20mobile%20app%2C%20available%20on%20both%20iOS%20and%20Android%20devices.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731256620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fau3ntol_exam-preparation_625x300_10_November_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fpreparing-for-jee-main-2025-explore-iit-kanpurs-45-day-crash-course-6987880%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22JEE%20Main%202025%3A%20IIT%20Kanpur's%20SATHEE%20platform%20also%20has%20a%20set%20of%20mock%20tests%20that%20help%20students%20replicate%20actual%20exam%20conditions%2C%20boost%20their%20confidence%2C%20and%20assess%20their%20readiness%20for%20the%20test.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India%20Not%20Among%20Nations%20Nervous%20About%20US%20After%20Trump's%20Return%3A%20S%20Jaishankar%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20a%20trend%20towards%20a%20more%20diverse%2C%20multipolar%20world%20but%20older%2C%20industrialised%20economies%20have%20not%20gone%20away%20and%20remain%20prime%20investment%20targets%2C%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20said%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20at%20the%20silver%20jubilee%20celebrations%20of%20the%20Aditya%20Birla%20Group's%20Scholarships%20programme%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20S%20Jaishankar%20said%20while%20a%20lot%20of%20countries%20are%20nervous%20about%20the%20US%20--%20following%20the%20return%20of%20Donald%20Trump%20as%20President%20--%20India%20is%20not%20one%20among%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYes%2C%20there%20is%20a%20shift.%20We%20are%20ourselves%20an%20example%20of%20the%20shift...%20if%20you%20look%20at%20our%20economic%20weight%2C%20you%20look%20at%20our%20economic%20ranking%2C%20you%20look%20at%20even%20Indian%20corporates%2C%20their%20reach%2C%20their%20presence%2C%20Indian%20professionals%2C%20which%20I%20spoke%20about.%20So%20no%20question%20there%20is%20a%20rebalancing%2C%26quot%3B%20S%20Jaishankar%20said%20in%20response%20to%20a%20question%20on%20the%20reset%20in%20the%20global%20power%20dynamic%20that%20was%20playing%20out%20amid%20the%20shift%20in%20the%20balance%20of%20power%20from%20the%20west%20to%20the%20east.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20to%20my%20mind%2C%20it%20was%20inevitable%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3Bbecause%20once%20these%20countries%20after%20the%20colonial%20period%20got%20their%20independence%2C%20they%20started%20making%20their%20own%20policy%20choices%2C%20then%20they%20were%20bound%20to%20grow.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BThe%20part%20which%20is%20not%20inevitable%20is%20that%20some%20grew%20faster%2C%20some%20grew%20slower%2C%20some%20grew%20better%2C%20and%20there%20the%20quality%20of%20governance%20and%20the%20quality%20of%20leadership%20came%20in.%20So%2C%20there%20is%2C%20in%20a%20sense%2C%20therefore%2C%20the%20constant%20and%20the%20variable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20a%20trend%20towards%20a%20more%20diverse%2C%20multipolar%20world.%20But%20there%20is%20also%2C%20you%20know%2C%20a%20period%20when%20countries%20really%20surge%20ahead.%20I%20mean%2C%20it's%20like%20what%20happened%20in%20the%20corporate%20world%20as%20well.%26quot%3B%20He%2C%20however%2C%20said%20the%20industrialised%20economies%20in%20the%20west%20cannot%20be%20ignored%20and%20remain%20prime%20investment%20targets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20do%20remember%20one%20thing%2C%20the%20older%2C%20the%20western%20economies%2C%20the%20older%20industrialised%20economies%2C%20they%20have%20not%20gone%20away.%20They%20still%20count%2C%20they%20are%20still%20prime%20investment%20targets.%20They%20are%20big%20markets%2C%20strong%20technology%20centres%2C%20hubs%20for%20innovation.%20So%20let's%20recognise%20the%20shift%2C%20but%20let's%20not%20get%20carried%20away%20and%20kind%20of%20overstate%20it%20and%20distort%20our%20own%20understanding%20of%20the%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20on%20the%20India-US%20relationship%20and%20Trump's%20win%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20was%20among%20the%20first%20three%20calls%2C%20I%20think%2C%20that%20President%20(elect)%20Trump%20took.%26quot%3B%20India%20and%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20have%20built%20rapport%20with%20multiple%20presidents%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20him%20(PM%20Modi)%20there's%20something%20natural%20in%20terms%20of%20how%20he%20forges%20those%20relationships.%20So%20that's%20helped%20hugely.%20And%20I%20think%20the%20changes%20in%20India%20have%20helped%20as%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20when%20asked%20how%20he%20sees%20the%20US%20presidential%20election%20outcome%20impacting%20India-US%20ties%2C%20especially%20given%20PM%20Modi's%20strong%20personal%20rapport%20with%20the%20US%20President-elect.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20know%20today%20a%20lot%20of%20countries%20are%20nervous%20about%20the%20US%2C%20let's%20be%20honest%20about%20it.%20We%20are%20not%20one%20of%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20S%20Jaishankar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20Aditya%20Birla%20Group%20Chairman%20Kumar%20Mangalam%20Birla%20said%20investment%20in%20talent%20is%20what%20shapes%20the%20future%2C%20and%20emphasised%20that%20with%20the%20scholarship%20programme%2C%20%26quot%3Bwe%20were%20driven%20by%20the%20ambition%20to%20create%20a%20cadre%20of%20handpicked%20leaders%20who%20would%20excel%20in%20India%20and%20also%20represent%20our%20country%20abroad%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Aditya%20Birla%20Scholarship%20is%20a%20tribute%20to%20my%20father's%20legacy%20and%20an%20ode%20to%20the%20spirit%20of%20ambition%20and%20extraordinary%20determination%20that%20defines%20India.%20With%20this%20scholarship%20programme%2C%20we%20were%20driven%20by%20the%20ambition%20to%20create%20a%20cadre%20of%20handpicked%20leaders%20who%20would%20excel%20in%20India%20and%20also%20represent%20our%20country%20abroad%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETerming%20the%20scholarship%20a%20microcosm%20of%20India's%20immense%20talent%20--%20abundant%20and%20outstanding%20--%20Birla%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20extraordinary%20success%20of%20the%20programme%2C%20as%20measured%20by%20the%20achievements%20of%20our%20scholars%20over%20the%20years%2C%20only%20indicates%20that%20ultimately%20investment%20in%20talent%20is%20what%20shapes%20the%20future.%26quot%3B%20Established%20in%201999%20in%20memory%20of%20late%20industrialist%20Aditya%20Vikram%20Birla%2C%20the%20programme%20has%20emerged%20as%20one%20of%20India's%20most-coveted%20merit-based%20scholarships%2C%20according%20to%20the%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20programme%20partners%20with%2022%20premier%20institutions%2C%20including%20select%20IITS%2C%20BITS%20Pilani%2C%20leading%20IIMS%2C%20XLRI%2C%20and%20national%20law%20schools.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20its%2025-year%20journey%2C%20over%2010%2C000%20applications%20have%20been%20evaluated%20by%20a%20team%20of%20experts%2C%20maintaining%20a%20steadfast%20commitment%20to%20excellence%20and%20diversity.%20The%20total%20number%20of%20Aditya%20Birla%20Scho