harashtra%20minister%20last%20month%20-%20was%20caught%20in%20a%20joint%20operation%20of%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20Mumbai%20police%20from%20Nanpara%20area%20of%20Bahraich.%C2%A0%20Shiv%20Kumar%2C%20the%20police%20said%2C%20is%20one%20of%20the%20three%20shooters%20and%20also%20the%20person%20who%20was%20in%20touch%20with%20the%20Lawrence%20Bishnoi%20gang.%20All%20instructions%20from%20the%20gang%20were%20routed%20through%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20sources%20said%20Shiv%20Kumar%20admitted%20during%20interrogation%20that%20he%20is%20linked%20to%20the%20Lawrence%20BIshnoi%20gang.%20The%20murder%2C%20he%20allegedly%20said%2C%20was%20carried%20out%20on%20the%20instructions%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsalman-khan-baba-siddique-sidhu-moosewala-who-is-anmol-bishnoi-lawrence-bishnois-brother-and-accused-in-key-cases-6871583%5C%22%3EAnmol%20Bishnoi%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20brother%20of%20Lawrence%20Bishnoi%2C%20who%20is%20believed%20to%20be%20living%20in%20Canada.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnmol%20Bishnoi's%20name%20has%20cropped%20up%20in%20the%20murder%20of%20Punjabi%20singer-politician%20Sidhu%20Moosewala%20in%202022%2C%20and%20the%20firing%20outside%20actor%20Salman%20Khan's%20residence%20in%20Mumbai%20in%20April.%20He%20is%20on%20the%20most-wanted%20list%20of%20the%20National%20Investigation%20Agency%20and%20a%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20reward%20has%20been%20announced%20for%20his%20arrest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20his%20interrogation%2C%20Shiv%20Kumar%20apparently%20said%20they%20were%20in%20Mumbai%20for%20days%20conducting%20recce%20for%20Baba%20Siddique%20and%20on%20the%20night%20of%20October%2012%2C%20%26quot%3BWhen%20we%20got%20the%20right%20time%2C%20we%20killed%20Baba%20Siddiqui%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20being%20a%20day%20of%20festival%2C%20the%20road%20was%20crowded%20and%20two%20of%20the%20attackers%20got%20caught%20but%20Shiv%20Kumar%20managed%20to%20escape.%20%C2%A0%26quot%3BI%20threw%20out%20the%20phone%20on%20the%20way%20and%20went%20from%20Mumbai%20to%20Pune.%20From%20Pune%2C%20I%20reached%20Bahraich%20via%20Jhansi%20and%20Lucknow%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20sources.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20asked%20for%20a%20phone%20from%20a%20passenger%20in%20the%20train%20and%20talked%20to%20Anurag%20Kashyap%2C%20he%20said%20Avindra%2C%20Gyan%20Prakash%20and%20Akash%20have%20made%20arrangements%20for%20me%20to%20hide%20in%20Nepal.%20That%20is%20why%20I%20came%20to%20Bahraich%20and%20was%20trying%20to%20escape%20to%20Nepal%20along%20with%20my%20companions%2C%26quot%3B%20sources%20quoted%20him%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20murder%20of%20Baba%20Siddiqui%2C%20Shiv%20Kumar%20had%20to%20go%20to%20Omkareshwar%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20to%20meet%20some%20henchmen%20of%20gang.%20The%20Mumbai%20police%20had%20tracked%20him%20to%20Omkareshwar%20but%20failed%20to%20catch%20him..%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBaba%20Siddique%20was%20shot%20down%20apparently%20because%20of%20his%20close%20relationship%20with%20Bollywood%20actor%20Salman%20Khan.%20Bishnoi's%20associates%20have%20hinted%20that%20the%20grouse%20against%20Salman%20Khan%20is%20about%20the%20blackbucks%20he%20killed%2020%20years%20ago.%20Blackbucks%20are%20sacred%20to%20the%20Bishnoi%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInvestigators%20said%20Baba%20Siddique's%20son%2C%20Mumbai%20MLA%20%C2%A0Zeeshan%20Siddique%2C%20is%20also%20a%20target%20for%20the%20same%20reason.%20His%20photo%20has%20been%20found%20on%20a%20cell%20phone%20seized%20from%20one%20of%20the%20three%20men%20who%20shot%20his%20father.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731254580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fg4hdg1r_baba-siddique_625x300_08_November_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmain-accused-on-the-run-in-baba-siddiques-murder-arrested-from-up-6987769%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Shivkumar%2C%20one%20of%20the%20three%20shooters%20in%20the%20Baba%20Siddi