20shared%20without%20showing%20the%20full%20context%20of%20what%20he%20said%2C%20top%20sources%20in%20the%20Mizoram%20government%20with%20direct%20knowledge%20of%20the%20matter%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20sections%20with%20an%20agenda%20are%20trying%20hard%20to%20malign%20both%20the%20Centre%20and%20the%20state%20government%2C%20sources%20said%2C%20adding%20legal%20action%20against%20them%20cannot%20be%20ruled%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Lalduhoma%20visited%20the%20US%20for%20a%20week%20beginning%20August%2030%2C%20and%20addressed%20the%20large%20Mizo%20community%20settled%20in%20the%20US%20on%20September%202%20and%204.%20Two%20months%20later%2C%20parts%20of%20his%20speech%20on%20the%20aspiration%20of%20the%20Zo%20people%20living%20in%20India%2C%20Bangladesh%20and%20Myanmar%20to%20be%20reunited%20under%20India%20went%20viral%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Lalduhoma%20towards%20the%20end%20of%20his%20address%20on%20September%204%20in%20Indianapolis%20had%20said%20the%20reason%20why%20he%20accepted%20the%20invitation%20from%20the%20diaspora%20to%20visit%20the%20US%20was%20to%20%26quot%3Bseek%20a%20path%20towards%20unity%20for%20all%20of%20us%26quot%3B%20and%20to%20%26quot%3B...%20rise%20together%20under%20one%20leadership%20to%20achieve%20our%20destiny%20of%20nationhood.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20a%20country%20may%20have%20borders%2C%20a%20true%20nation%20transcends%20such%20limitations.%20We%20have%20been%20unjustly%20divided%2C%20forced%20to%20exist%20under%20three%20different%20governments%20in%20three%20different%20countries%2C%20and%20this%20is%20something%20we%20can%20never%20accept%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Lalduhoma%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Agenda-Driven%20Attempts'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20told%20NDTV%20this%20comment%20has%20been%20made%20to%20go%20viral%20by%20sections%20who%20have%20an%20agenda%20when%20the%20nuances%20of%20the%20Chief%20Minister's%20address%20were%20very%20clear%20-%20i.e.%20nothing%20was%20said%20that%20was%20anti-India%3B%20on%20the%20contrary%20the%20Chief%20Minister's%20full%20text%20of%20the%20speeches%20show%20a%20culturally%20unifying%20call%20for%20the%20Zo%20people%20across%20borders%2C%20especially%20in%20Myanmar's%20Chin%20hills%20region%2C%20from%20where%20the%20junta%20has%20been%20pushed%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Ffvefgs5o_mizoram-generic_625x300_10_November_24.jpg%3Fim%3DFeatureCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20September%204%20speech%20that%20mentioned%20%26quot%3Bnationhood%26quot%3B%20is%20on%20the%20same%20lines%20as%20the%20September%202%20address%20where%20Mr%20Lalduhoma%20clearly%20spoke%20about%20the%20desire%20of%20the%20Zo%20people%20for%20unification%20under%20India%2C%20sources%20said%2C%20adding%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20also%20mentioned%20about%20the%20%26quot%3Bgeopolitical%20realities%26quot%3B%20at%20present.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20in%20the%20nation's%20interest%20to%20have%20peace%20in%20the%20region.%20The%20Zo%20people%20living%20across%20the%20borders%20have%20to%20be%20culturally%20united%20under%20India%20to%20withstand%20covert%20designs%20aimed%20at%20destabilising%20the%20region.%20That%20was%20the%20message%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20was%20giving%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20top%20source%20in%20the%20state%20government%20told%20NDTV%20in%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20least%20in%20theory%2C%20philosophically%2C%20even%20the%20controversial%20idea%20of%20an%20Akhand%20Bharat%20is%20a%20unifying%20idea%2C%20and%20the%20call%20for%20unification%20of%20cross-border%20peoples%20who%20share%20the%20same%20ethnic%20ties%20is%20well%20within%20that%20idea%2C%20which%20is%20not%20anti-national.%20This%20is%20all%20theoretical%2C%20but%20you%20get%20the%20point%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20source%2C%20adding%20those%20who%20are%20seeing%20a%20conspiracy%20where%20there%20is%20none%20should%20step%20back%20and%20take%20a%20relook%20at%20what%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20said%2C%20in%20the%20context%20of%20changing%20geopolitical%20realities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Centre%20Knows%20There's%20No%20Controversy'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20visit%20was%20cleared%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20(MEA)%2C%20Mr%20Lalduhomahad%20had%20said%20in%20his%20address%20in%20Maryland%20to%20celebrate%20Mizo%20Day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndian%20officials%20also%20attended%20the%20two%20events%2C%20and%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20ensured%20that%20printouts%20of%20the%20speeches%20translated%20into%20both%20Mizo%20and%20English%20were%20given%20to%20the%20attendees%20including%20the%20officials%2C%20the%20sources%20said%2C%20requesting%20anonymity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Lalduhoma%20had%20thanked%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20and%20Finance%20Minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20for%20the%20unconditional%20support%20they%20have%20been%20giving%20to%20Mizoram%20to%20handle%20the%20refugee%20crisis%20owing%20to%20the%20conflict%20in%20Myanmar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20text%20of%20the%20speeches%20has%20been%20on%20the%20Mizoram%20government's%20website%20for%20the%20last%20two%20months%2C%20until%20some%20vested%20interests%20brought%20it%20up%20and%20twisted%20it%20with%20a%20malicious%20intent%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fcfjgkhqo_mizoram-generic-unsplash_625x300_27_October_24.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20word%20'%3Cem%3Ehnam%3C%2Fem%3E'%20in%20Mizo%20was%20translated%20as%20'nationhood'%2C%20which%20is%20not.%20When%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20said%20land%20has%20borders%2C%20what%20he%20meant%20was%20community%2C%20ethnic%20group%20and%20blood%20relations%20don't%20have%20borders.%20But%20it%20was%20taken%20as%20literally%20meaning%20nationhood.%20So%20this%20was%20the%20primary%20misunderstanding%20of%20his%20speech%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20source%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20is%20very%20unfortunate%20is%20there%20seems%20to%20be%20some%20propaganda%20against%20us.%20Mr%20Lalduhoma%20was%20a%20former%20Indian%20Police%20Service%20officer%2C%20a%20former%20MP%2C%20a%20five-time%20MLA%20and%20now%20Chief%20Minister.%20His%20loyalty%20and%20commitment%20to%20the%20nation%20is%20second%20to%20none.%20He%20is%20probably%20the%20most%20qualified%20among%20all%20chief%20ministers%2C%20the%20most%20Indian%20for%20that%20matter.%20So%20thinking%20of%20him%20as%20a%20separatist%2C%20agenda-driven%20is%20just%20not%20possible%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20source%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20voices%20have%20to%20be%20heard.%20If%20the%20rhetoric%20continues%2C%20people%20will%20assume%20wrong%20things%20about%20our%20state...%20In%20his%20Maryland%20speech%2C%20he%20(Mr%20Lalduhoma)%20went%20on%20to%20say%20that%20if%20we%20were%20not%20part%20of%20India%20today%2C%20if%20Mizoram%20were%20to%20be%20independent%2C%20would%20we%20find%20another%20India%3F%20I%20don't%20think%20any%20other%20country%20would%20literally%20spoon%20feed%20us%2C%20take%20care%20of%20us%20like%20India%20is%20doing.%20He%20even%20gave%20the%20example%20of%20minorities%20in%20China.%20Look%20at%20the%20situation%20out%20there%20%5Bin%20China%5D.%20We%20are%20proud%20Indians%20today.%20That%20was%20really%20the%20message%20that%20he%20was%20trying%20to%20get%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20source%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20very%20clear%3B%20it%20is%20about%20reunification%20under%20India...%20This