society%20and%20therefore%2C%20the%20colleges%20have%20to%20be%20rejuvenated%20to%20create%20a%20positive%2C%20clean%2C%20healthy%20and%20educational%20environment%20in%20the%20colleges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20joint%20director%20further%20said%20in%20the%20order%20that%20in%20the%20first%20phase%20of%20the%20scheme%2C%20two%20government%20colleges%20of%20each%20division%20have%20been%20included%20and%20the%20front%20facade%20and%20entrance%20hall%20of%20the%2020%20colleges'%20buildings%20should%20be%20phase%20painted%20with%20%26quot%3BAsian%20Paints%20White%20Gold%208292%20and%20Asian%20Paints%20Orange%20Crown%207974%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETargeting%20the%20BJP%20government%20over%20the%20matter%2C%20PCC%20general%20secretary%20Swarnim%20Chaturvedi%20said%20that%20it%20was%20an%20attempt%20to%20%26quot%3Bpoliticise%26quot%3B%20education%20in%20colleges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20BJP%20government%20has%20failed%20to%20deliver%20on%20promises%20made%20to%20people.%20The%20government%20has%20nothing%20to%20highlight%20as%20its%20achievements%20and%20in%20order%20to%20divert%20attention%3B%20it%20is%20resorting%20to%20such%20moves%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731247860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2F5qj5hth8_rajasthan-college_625x300_10_November_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frajasthan-to-paint-20-government-college-gates-orange-congress-reacts-6987611%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Rajasthan%20College%20Education%20Commissionerate%20has%20directed%2020%20government%20colleges%20to%20get%20the%20front%20facade%20of%20their%20buildings%20and%20entry%20halls%20painted%20orange.%20Congress%20said%20that%20it%20was%20an%20attempt%20to%20%26quot%3Bpoliticise%26quot%3