%20matter...%20There%20is%20this%20saying%20--%20everything%20is%20fair%20in%20love%20and%20politics%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Gadkari%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20held%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20the%20opposition%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%20had%20won%2030%20of%20the%20state's%2048%20seats.%20The%20ruling%20alliance%20won%2017.%20One%20seat%20went%20to%20an%20Independent%20candidate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20results%20were%20seen%20as%20a%20reflection%20of%20the%20public%20disapproval%20of%20the%20political%20upheaval%20in%20the%20state%20--%20the%20split%20in%20Shiv%20Sena%2C%20the%20collapse%20of%20the%20MVA%20government%20and%20the%20passing%20of%20the%20reins%20of%20power%20to%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20rebel%20faction%20of%20the%20Sena.%20It%20was%20followed%20by%20the%20split%20in%20the%20Nationalist%20Congress%20party%20of%20Sharad%20Pawar%20and%20the%20rebel%20faction%20led%20by%20Ajit%20Pawar%20joining%20the%20ruling%20coalition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Opposition%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%20had%20won%2030%20of%20the%20state's%2048%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%2C%20the%20ruling%20alliance%20won%2017.%20The%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20faction%20of%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20won%20nine%20seats%2C%20ahead%20of%20the%207%20won%20by%20Mr%20Shinde's%20faction.%20The%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20-%20Sharadchandra%20Pawar%20-%20scooped%20up%20eight%20seats%2C%20compared%20to%20the%20one%20won%20by%20Ajit%20Pawar's%20party.%20The%20biggest%20winner%20was%20the%20Congress%2C%20which%20went%20up%20from%20one%20seat%20to%2013.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%2C%20seen%20as%20the%20instigator%2C%20had%20also%20suffered%2C%20sliding%20to%20nine%20seats%20from%20the%2023%20it%20won%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolling%20for%20the%20288-member%20Maharashtra%20assembly%20will%20be%20held%20in%20a%20single%20phase%20on%20November%2020%20and%20the%20counting%20of%20votes%20will%20be%20held%20on%20November%2023.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731245