0was%20too%20short%20to%20recognize%20the%20song.%20The%20staff%20let%20them%20play%20it%20a%20bit%20longer%2C%20and%20Gong%20Yoo%20got%20all%20worked%20up%20because%20he%20recognized%20the%20familiar%20tune%20but%20couldn't%20remember%20further%20particulars%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fweb-series%2Fnews%2Fkorean%2Fseo-hyun-jin-issues-dramatic-apology-to-bts-fans-heres-why%2Farticleshow%2F115141893.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mining%20tax%20by%20states%3A%20Tata%20Steel%20to%20file%20curative%20petition%20in%20Supreme%20Court%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731234171000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fmining-tax-levy-tata-steel-to-file-curative-petition-in-supreme-court-124111000271_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22On%20July%2025%2C%20a%20nine-judge%20Constitution%20Bench%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20ruled%20that%20states%20have%20the%20power%20to%20levy%20cess%20on%20mining%20and%20mineral-use%20activities.%20Tata%20Steel's%20petition%20seeks%20a%20remedy%20to%20this%20order%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BMadam%20Sonia%20Ji...%26quot%3B%3A%20PM%20Draws%20A%20Comparison%20On%20Centre's%20Support%20To%20Jharkhand%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20and%20its%20allies%20want%20to%20divide%20the%20OBC%20community%20by%20pitting%20sub-castes%20against%20each%20other%20for%20political%20gains%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20alleged%20today.%20Addressing%20an%20election%20rally%20in%20Jharkhand's%20Bokaro%2C%20he%20used%20the%20slogan%3A%20%26quot%3BEk%20rahenge%20toh%20safe%20rahenge%26quot%3B.%20The%20slogan%2C%20which%20means%20%26quot%3Bwe%20will%20be%20safe%20if%20we%20are%20united%26quot%3B%2C%20appealed%20to%20the%20backward%20castes%20to%20stay%20united.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said%2C%20has%20not%20been%20able%20to%20cross%20the%20250%20mark%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20after%20the%20OBC%20community%20got%20reservation%20in%20the%2090s.%20%26quot%3BSo%20the%20Congress%20wants%20to%20break%20the%20OBC%20community%20and%20divide%20them%20into%20numerous%20castes%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20unity%20of%20castes%20under%20the%20OBC%20umbrella%2C%20he%20said%2C%20has%20made%20the%20country%20stronger.%20%26quot%3BBut%20the%20Congress%20and%20JMM%20want%20to%20make%20them%20fight%20among%20themselves.%20They%20want%20that%20castes%20in%20OBC%20category%20stop%20considering%20themselves%20OBC%20and%20remain%20entangled%20in%20their%20own%20castes.%20I%20want%20to%20ask%20you%2C%20do%20you%20want%20the%20OBC%20community%20to%20disintegrate%3F%20Won't%20your%20voice%20become%20weaker%20if%20you%20break%3F%20We%20have%20to%20remember%2C%20'ek%20rahenge%20toh%20safe%20rahenge'%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20said%20many%20youths%20from%20Jharkhand%20are%20in%20the%20Army.%20%26quot%3BWe%20lost%20many%20jawans%20due%20to%20terrorism%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%20A%20big%20reason%20was%20the%20wall%20of%20Article%20370.%20Modi%20has%20buried%20that%20wall%20for%20ever.%20But%20the%20Congress%20and%20its%20allies%20don't%20like%20this.%20You%20may%20not%20know%20this.%20The%20country%20became%20Independent%2C%20got%20a%20Constitution%2C%20but%20for%20seven%20decades%2C%20BR%20Ambedkar's%20Constitution%20was%20not%20implemented%2C%20Dalits%20and%20Adivasis%20did%20not%20get%20reservation%20there.%20Modi%20has%20demolished%20the%20Article%20370%20wall%20and%20took%20BR%20Ambedkar's%20Constitution%20there.%20You%20must%20have%20seen%2C%20elections%20took%20place%20and%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Chief%20Minister%20took%20oath%20on%20Babasaheb%20Ambedkar's%20Constitution.%20This%20is%20Modi's%20tribute%20to%20Babasaheb%20Ambedkar%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20the%20uproar%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Assembly%20over%20a%20resolution%20to%20restore%20special%20status%20under%20Article%20370%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BAs%20soon%20as%20they%20formed%20the%20government%2C%20Congress%20and%20its%20allies%20have%20started%20playing%20their%20games%2C%20they%20passed%20a%20resolution%20to%20bring%20Article%20370%20back.%20JMM%20is%20also%20supporting%20them.%20They%20want%20to%20remove%20BR%20Ambedkar's%20Constitution%20from%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20again.%20They%20want%20to%20deprive%20Dalits%2C%20backward%20classes%20and%20Adivasis.%20They%20want%20to%20throw%20our%20soldiers%20into%20the%20fire%20of%20terror.%20I%20want%20to%20ask%20you%2C%20do%20you%20accept%20this%20sin%20by%20the%20Congress%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20said%20the%20BJP%20would%20stop%20infiltration%20into%20the%20state.%20He%20said%20Jharkhand%20needs%20an%20NDA%20government%20to%20ensure%20the%20safety%20of%20its%20daughters%20and%20land%20owned%20by%20people.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20to%20build%20a%20Jharkhand%20that%20is%20counted%20among%20the%20most%20prosperous%20in%20the%20country.%20I%20have%20come%20to%20seek%20your%20help%20and%20blessings.%20You%20have%20to%20make%20candidates%20of%20BJP%2C%20AJSU%2C%20LJP%20and%20JDU%20win%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20accused%20the%20ruling%20JMM%20and%20Congress%20of%20creating%20a%20%26quot%3Bpaper%20leak%20mafia%26quot%3B%20and%20a%20%26quot%3Brecruitment%20mafia%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BWe%20will%20strike%20all%20those%20involved.%20We%20will%20dig%20them%20out%20of%20the%20underworld%20and%20send%20them%20to%20jail%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20Leaks%20of%20question%20papers%20