kka3-1730299644.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D373638%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Pakka%20Limited%2C%20started%20by%20K%20K%20Jhunjhunwala%20in%20Ayodhya%20in%201981%2C%20has%20transformed%20into%20a%20compostable%20packaging%20business%2C%20with%20a%20yearly%20production%20capacity%20of%2050%2C000%20tonnes.%20Their%20factory%20is%20powered%20by%20rice%20husk%20where%20they%20recover%2095%20percent%20of%20chemicals%20used!%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F373638%2Fyash-pakka-ltd-ved-krishna-chuk-compostable-packaging-sustainable-products%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22One%20Family%E2%80%99s%20Struggle%20is%20Changing%20Dialysis%20Care%20%26amp%3B%20Making%20It%20More%20Easily%20Available%20In%20Tier%202%20%26amp%3B%203%20Cities%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhen%20Prabhat%20Shrivastava%E2%80%99s%20father%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20chronic%20kidney%20disease%20(CKD)%20and%20advised%20to%20start%20dialysis%2C%20the%20family%20faced%20a%20significant%20decision.%20Residing%20in%20Jabalpur%2C%20Prabhat%20was%20disappointed%20with%20the%20available%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F336026%2Fdr-sudhir-srivastava-made-in-india-surgical-robot-cheaper-surgeries-affordable-healthcare-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20dialysis%20facilities%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20his%20hometown%20and%20encouraged%20his%20parents%20to%20move%20with%20him%20to%20Gurgaon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20relocation%20took%20a%20huge%20toll%20on%20the%20family%20and%20led%20to%20many%20conversations%20around%20the%20lack%20of%20access%20to%20good%20dialysis%20care%20in%20India.%20As%20Prabhat%20discussed%20this%20with%20his%20father%E2%80%99s%20nephrologist%2C%20Dr%20Saurabh%20Pokhariyal%2C%20they%20knew%20that%20they%20had%20to%20address%20this%20gap.%20Ano