0in%20the%20West%2C%20patients%20live%20for%20over%2015%20years.%20We%20need%20to%20improve%20outcomes%20for%20our%20country%2C%E2%80%9D%20emphasises%20Prabhat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChronic%20kidney%20disease%20(CKD)%20affects%20a%20significant%20portion%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20population%2C%20although%20the%20exact%20number%20of%20patients%20remains%20unknown.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201000px)%20100vw%2C%201000px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-2024-10-30T195140.909-1730298116.jpg%3Ffit%3D1200%252C628%26quality%3D89%26ssl%3D1%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Founders%20Prabhat%20Shrivastava%2C%20Pankaj%20Tandon%20and%20Dr%20Saurabh%20Pokhariyal%20(L-R)%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-2024-10-30T195140.909-1730298116.jpg%3Fw%3D1200%26amp%3Bquality%3D89%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-2024-10-30T195140.909-1730298116.jpg%3Fresize%3D300%252C157%26amp%3Bquality%3D89%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-2024-10-30T195140.909-1730298116.jpg%3Fresize%3D500%252C262%26amp%3Bquality%3D89%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-2024-10-30T195140.909-1730298116.jpg%3Fresize%3D768%252C402%26amp%3Bquality%3D89%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-2024-10-30T195140.909-1730298116.jpg%3Fresize%3D150%252C79%26amp%3Bquality%3D89%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-373632%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-ele