es%2C%20nephrologists%2C%20operations%20teams%2C%20and%20teams%20that%20focus%20on%20increasing%20awareness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20mission%20is%20to%20bring%20dialysis%20centres%20near%20the%20patients%E2%80%99%20home%2C%20minimising%20travel.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVitusCare%20provides%20free%20dialysis%20for%20patients%20under%20the%20Ayushman%20Bharat%20scheme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20problem%20with%20kidney%20disease%20is%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20difficult%20to%20reverse.%20%E2%80%9COnce%20the%20kidney%20has%20failed%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20failed.%20You%20can%E2%80%99t%20cure%20CKD%20stage%20two%20or%20three%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Prabhat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPatients%20have%20two%20options%3A%20opting%20for%20kidney%20transplants%20or%20undergoing%20dialysis.%20The%20former%20is%20expensive%20and%20comes%20with%20the%20added%20problem%20of%20lack%20of%20donors.%20For%20most%20patients%2C%20dialysis%20becomes%20the%20only%20viable%20option%20to%20ensure%20a%20good%20quality%20of%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMissing%20dialysis%20sessions%20can%20lead%20to%20serious%20health%20complications%20as%20waste%20and%20fluids%20build%20up%20in%20the%20body.%20High%20potassium%20levels%20can%20disrupt%20heart%20rhythm%20and%20become%20life-threatening.%20Fluid%20overload%20may%20cause%20fluid%20retention%20in%20the%20lungs%2C%20leading%20to%20breathlessness%2C%20swollen%20ankles%2C%20high%20blood%20pressure%2C%20and%20even%20heart%20failure.%20Patients%20may%20also%20experience%20intense%20itching%2C%20extreme%20fatigue%2C%20and%20reduced%20appetite%2C%20further%20weakening%20their%20overall%20health.%20Regular%20dialysis%20is%20essential%20to%20manage%20these%20risks%20and%20maintain%20stability%20for%20those%20with%20kidney%20failure%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Dr%20Saurabh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInitially%20bootstrapped%2C%20the%20founders%20recently%20managed%20to%20raise%20a%20Series%20A%20round%20of%20investment.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20currently%20have%20centres%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Uttarakhand%2C%20Haryana%2C%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20Punjab%2C%20Delhi%2C%20Rajasthan%20and%20plan%20to%20deepen%20their%20presence%20in%20these%20states.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20journey%20has%20been%20very%20satisfying%20and%20full%20of%20learning.%20We%20want%20to%20provide%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F250227%2Fshashank-moddhia-mumbai-startup-renal-project-affordable-kidney-dialysis-in-india-healthcare-him16%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ekidney%20disease%20patients%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewith%20a%20better%20quality%20of%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20concludes%20Prabhat.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESources%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thelancet.com%2Fjournals%2Flanglo%2Farticle%2FPIIS2214-109X(16)30308-4%2Ffulltext%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERenal%20failure%20deaths%20and%20their%20risk%20factors%20in%20India%202001%E2%80%9313%3A%20nationally%20representative%20estimates%20from%20the%20Million%20Death%20Study%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20by%20The%20Lancet%20Global%20Health%2C%20Published%20in%20January%202017.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pmndp.mohfw.gov.in%2Fen%2Fintroduction-of-pradhan-mantri-national-dialysis-program-pmndp%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPradhan%20Mantri%20National%20Dialysis%20Program%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20by%20Ministry%20of%20Health%20%26amp%3B%20Family%20Welfare%2C%20Government%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Arunava%20Banerjee%2C%20Images%20Courtesy%20Prabhat%20Shrivastava%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730604600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.t